The paper discusses the security and dependability of IoT systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also focuses on the cyber-physical systems (CPSs) and their monitoring and control, which is related to networked systems (cs.NI) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses fault-tolerance and self-healing, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
